"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:25:54.000Z","msg":"你話留比黑警搞根本冇可能<br />\n過多排比鄧炳強呢隻牛屎佬做埋一哥<br />\n你覺得佢地仲會點搞<br />\n而且所謂民兵團要組成難度太高<br />\n唔係人人都可以24小時on call<br />\n而加個情況係中共製造出黎<br />\n目的要我地怕佢<br />\n所以我地先要出黎話比佢知<br />\n我地係唔會怕<br />\n催淚彈橡膠彈布袋彈都經歷過<br />\n會怕你班牛屎佬？<br />\n而且你覺得我地幾十萬人一齊出黎安全<br />\n定係靠100人嘅民兵團安全"},{"pid":"578c47ce4d1ceac0903b5e1fb7e6ad43865d0dc3","tid":1352641,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:26:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"236f6ad93c3098a0b63ecf5bf3d4e91a11a10658","tid":1352641,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8252e67a726db9c2d9f16daebdfbd3665f8678da","tid":1352641,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:27:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"306820c0863b919bdd42e14920f4b4f5220087d7","tid":1352641,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bd8933b1e7588f6828fca9ea0f377ee5743d7f","tid":1352641,"uid":257622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:28:25.000Z","msg":"入元朗個性質唔止係示威，而係反恐戰爭"},{"pid":"e1d35dfb740764c65a64ed95006f94c36d05d443","tid":1352641,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48e82a1f93c1ba3a1af1b0bbae4a134d1922965","tid":1352641,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\